{"id":2017,"date":"2022-04-17T10:06:28","date_gmt":"2022-04-17T07:06:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/?p=2017"},"modified":"2022-04-17T10:06:28","modified_gmt":"2022-04-17T07:06:28","slug":"sky-mavis-launch-1m-bug-bounty-program-for-cybersecurity-vigilantes","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/sky-mavis-launch-1m-bug-bounty-program-for-cybersecurity-vigilantes\/","title":{"rendered":"Sky Mavis Launch $1M Bug Bounty Program for Cybersecurity Vigilantes"},"content":{"rendered":"<p> <br \/>\n<\/p>\n<div itemprop=\"mainEntityOfPage\">\n<p>To kick off its recently announced $150 million Ronin Bridge breach <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/nftplazas.com\/150-million-fund-raised-to-recover-sky-mavis-ronin-bridge-breach\/\">reimbursement program<\/a>, Sky Mavis have decided to adopt a \u2018if you can\u2019t beat them, ask them\u2019 approach, as it will be offering up to $1 million to \u2018white hats\u2019 (a.k.a cybersecurity vigilantes)<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span>who can identify and disclose information on the security vulnerabilities of its network.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>The Axie Infinity developers took to <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/psycheout86\/status\/1513721129885704197?s=21&amp;t=WhsltcTG3tV5BKKMSVc_nw\">Twitter<\/a> to announce \u2018The Sky Mavis Bug Bounty Program,\u2019 where it stated that it\u2019ll follow a six month vesting period with monthly unlocks for fatal bounties dynamic, <strong>where rewards will be issued in $AXS<\/strong>, the native token of Axie Infinity.<\/p>\n<p>As there is a broad array of vulnerabilities to be highlighted, the scheme will entail different rewards depending on the stature of issue identified, with the company outlining that the top bounty of $1,000,000 will go to those who can identify \u201cextraordinarily severe issues or those with extreme impact\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>A further $100,000 will go to those who can identify <strong>critical smart contract and blockchain vulnerabilities<\/strong>, and bounties ranging from $50,000 to $50 will go to those who can identify risks which are deemed high, medium, and low.<\/p>\n<p>Ironically, the company have also had to ask those participating to not use the program to leverage spam, spoof, and phishing attacks on the Axie community, whilst also stating that it will not issue rewards if findings are shared on social media.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nftplazas\/\">Follow us on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n<p><small><em>*All investment\/financial opinions expressed by NFT Plazas are from the personal research and experience of our site moderators and are intended as educational material only. Individuals are required to fully research any product prior to making any kind of investment.<\/em><\/small><\/p>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"author\">\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-tab\">\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-gravatar\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-desc\">\n<div itemprop=\"description\">\n<p>Team Writer. 100% Non-Fungible.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<p><script async src=\"\/\/platform.twitter.com\/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"